Title: A Simple Data Management and Sharing Tool
biocViews: DataImport, DataRepresentation, ThirdPartyClient
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Régis",
           family = "Ongaro-Carcy",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "ctb"),
